Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.78,0:00:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣一口氣直接衝進最後一集喔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.48,0:00:08.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…哈？最後一集？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.12,0:00:10.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才剛出場耶～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.76,0:00:15.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女武神核心被破壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.06,0:00:17.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,核心控制下的奴獸已被消滅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.73,0:00:19.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女武神部隊全部機能停止
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.50,0:00:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遊戲到此為止了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.70,0:00:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以這座城市為新大陸\N讓一切結束吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.70,0:00:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳懂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.17,0:00:31.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們已經無法回頭了唷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.01,0:00:35.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝爾蓋…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.05,0:00:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,體貼的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.71,0:00:40.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,體貼過頭的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.09,0:00:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過，我現在要感謝你的體貼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.39,0:00:49.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感謝你留力量給我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.23,0:00:52.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了你的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.83,0:00:54.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.14,0:01:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古風琴…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.34,0:01:08.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.95,0:01:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太陽…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.35,0:01:17.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被黑暗吞噬了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.69,0:01:26.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.86,0:01:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,物質化
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.20,0:01:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,物質化
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.99,0:01:55.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第26話\NDream☆Wing～夢想所在～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.63,0:01:58.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.49,0:02:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凪打算把這座城市一起毀掉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.63,0:02:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.63,0:02:02.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我辦不到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.93,0:02:04.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我約定好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.53,0:02:08.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要創造一個\N大家都能笑口常開的國家
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.34,0:02:10.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我不會逃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.34,0:02:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會再逃避了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.01,0:02:15.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白，把生命交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.21,0:02:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道方法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.91,0:02:19.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我得行動
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.28,0:02:21.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為妮娜在哭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.25,0:02:24.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.92,0:02:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的性命與妳同在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.66,0:02:28.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們上，愛莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.79,0:02:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾之乙HiME啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.60,0:02:38.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.63,0:02:39.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別勉強
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.84,0:02:41.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算蒼天的力量覺醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.00,0:02:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只靠妳一個人還是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.71,0:02:45.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我稍微活躍一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.68,0:02:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是，一上場就做苦工啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.51,0:02:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.15,0:02:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得到青色貴石的真正力量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.55,0:02:57.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得到一同前進的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.22,0:02:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.49,0:03:01.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我實踐妳最後的遺言吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.20,0:03:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引導之星呀，就是現在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.75,0:03:23.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.01,0:03:25.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.21,0:03:28.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個傳說竟然是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.18,0:03:32.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當引導之星閃耀紅光時
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.12,0:03:33.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部的乙HiME…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.69,0:03:35.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將擺脫“乙式”的限制
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.73,0:03:38.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.06,0:03:41.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深優真的做了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.63,0:03:45.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.30,0:03:46.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乙HiME們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.64,0:03:49.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在將妳們
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.14,0:03:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從命運之軛解放開來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.02,0:04:02.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞鬥服竟在沒認證下…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.89,0:04:04.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請選擇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.12,0:04:05.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以妳們自己的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.79,0:04:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,選擇該做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.19,0:04:10.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事到現在還用問嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.09,0:04:12.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出擊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.83,0:04:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦，唉呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.76,0:04:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.73,0:04:19.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等，慢著啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.14,0:04:27.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅莎麗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.98,0:04:29.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏樹姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.45,0:04:30.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡就交給…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.91,0:04:32.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我·們·吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.15,0:04:40.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下，也請讓我們加入您的麾下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.06,0:04:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.19,0:04:43.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我們不能以自己的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.99,0:04:45.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決定現在該做什麼的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.03,0:04:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.00,0:04:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也要幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.20,0:04:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.13,0:04:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要…唉呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.07,0:05:00.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.24,0:05:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們會撐住的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.51,0:05:03.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.95,0:05:04.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.08,0:05:06.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了，乙HiME們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.62,0:05:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.35,0:05:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奪回城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.49,0:05:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阻止那座古風琴！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.06,0:05:14.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.02,0:05:16.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢著啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.56,0:05:21.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好賊喔，那是犯規吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.63,0:05:23.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城市北邊出現新的艦隊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.07,0:05:25.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.03,0:05:26.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是卡迪亞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.48,0:05:41.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於連退路也沒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.78,0:05:44.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓原始奴獸全部啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.12,0:05:50.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（遵從黑色誓約，我將實現盟約）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.93,0:05:54.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（古代之光，知識與智慧之神啊）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.23,0:05:56.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（請賜我忠實的奴僕吧）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.00,0:06:00.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡交給我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.47,0:06:02.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏樹妳們到城裡去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.34,0:06:03.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜留，拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.21,0:06:06.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乙HiME需要的是力量，技巧和…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.88,0:06:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毅力！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.51,0:06:09.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.29,0:06:21.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了\N來把過去的比試了斷一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.69,0:06:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比比看誰打倒得最多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.89,0:06:26.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳還真是沒變呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.48,0:06:41.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘管來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.01,0:06:45.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我把你們一網大魔神
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.48,0:06:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小遙\N我已經不知道妳要講什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.02,0:06:49.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？閣下？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.09,0:06:51.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.25,0:06:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海拉德少尉，這給妳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.16,0:06:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已確實收到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.59,0:06:56.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在此準備進城
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.87,0:07:10.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡，妮娜就交給妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.67,0:07:11.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.41,0:07:17.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅色捲捲藍色捲捲黃色捲捲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.15,0:07:24.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳穿上舞鬥服根本沒意義嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.89,0:07:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是漩渦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.69,0:07:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茱麗葉妳閉嘴！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.97,0:07:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪亞姊姊？五柱的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.21,0:07:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茜？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.07,0:07:47.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等，妳還是乙HiME啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.18,0:07:51.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直被追著
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.55,0:07:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易終於有機會了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.88,0:07:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是阿和\N卻得繼位成為卡迪亞王而被帶走
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.45,0:08:00.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我則被瑪亞姊姊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.72,0:08:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳被逮捕了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.66,0:08:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正，讓她跟阿和陛下締結契約
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.33,0:08:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是抵銷了這次的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.30,0:08:10.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能接受
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.17,0:08:11.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對不讓妳們上床
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.00,0:08:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對不死心！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.47,0:08:15.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得這有點…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.92,0:08:28.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.79,0:08:33.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算過了這麼久\N妳還是有欠優雅呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.09,0:08:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.97,0:08:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪莉亞女士？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.50,0:08:45.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可嘆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.80,0:08:48.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好不容易老到理想年齡了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.67,0:08:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在居然還得現出這副模樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.14,0:08:55.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衝啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.41,0:08:57.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葵！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.05,0:09:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.52,0:09:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千繪…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.66,0:09:10.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連這種地方都…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.69,0:09:12.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.03,0:09:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去將編織者…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.60,0:09:17.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將妮娜從古風琴上解放開來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.90,0:09:19.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要快點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.13,0:09:22.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那座管風琴\N要是演奏太久會有危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.21,0:09:33.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地下通路有舞鬥服反應
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.55,0:09:34.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是蒼天的青玉！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.69,0:09:38.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.85,0:09:39.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.56,0:09:47.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎妳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.66,0:09:49.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.47,0:09:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凪…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.04,0:09:54.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜，快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.87,0:09:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.41,0:09:58.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是停下古風琴的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.34,0:10:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親就會死
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.18,0:10:09.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親為了我捨棄自己的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.25,0:10:10.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以這次…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.52,0:10:13.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會賭上我的一切！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.39,0:10:14.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守護父親！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.49,0:10:17.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.83,0:10:19.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想大概…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.83,0:10:22.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.60,0:10:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝爾蓋一定會說他並不想\N為了求生而害妮娜做出這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.90,0:10:30.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳又知道什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.17,0:10:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟父親的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.08,0:10:36.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳知道些什麼啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.28,0:10:43.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.06,0:10:49.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.47,0:10:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.07,0:11:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我稍微…知道喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.47,0:11:08.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也喜歡…謝爾蓋啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.91,0:11:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當我察覺到自己的心意時
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.35,0:11:16.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒辦法思考其他事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.55,0:11:19.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜的心情也是…什麼都是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.06,0:11:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那妳應該知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.72,0:11:23.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算犧牲一切
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.26,0:11:25.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算拿世界來交換
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.39,0:11:28.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想要那個人！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.34,0:11:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…我絕對要阻止妳！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.42,0:11:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.79,0:11:51.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.79,0:11:55.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們只能在一旁守著她們了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.12,0:11:56.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下就要靠她們自己了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.86,0:12:02.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是諷刺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.33,0:12:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果還是得將世界的結局\N交給乙HiME之間的戰爭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.20,0:12:09.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過契約好像解除了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.54,0:12:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就只能看戲了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.01,0:12:12.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.04,0:12:15.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不打算只讓愛莉卡奮鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.78,0:12:18.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凪，停止古風琴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.78,0:12:19.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.81,0:12:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個只聽妮娜的指揮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.62,0:12:24.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為她是真正的公主
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.65,0:12:28.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想把這個世界\N恢復成原本的模樣喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.42,0:12:30.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳也覺得很奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.29,0:12:33.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犧牲乙HiME，又封印科學
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.66,0:12:34.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.96,0:12:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.43,0:12:39.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然這星球\N曾因為這玩意兒毀滅過一次
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.84,0:12:50.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次我會好好照顧它的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.88,0:12:52.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,免得它失敗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.45,0:12:54.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.88,0:12:56.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣什麼都沒改變到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.62,0:12:58.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然要怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.32,0:12:59.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走回頭路？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.85,0:13:00.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.99,0:13:02.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科學也要漸漸開放
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.99,0:13:06.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天會不需要乙HiME
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.23,0:13:09.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那不會是你多管閒事下的產物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.76,0:13:10.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.90,0:13:12.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得要有人管理
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.00,0:13:13.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,囉嗦…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.64,0:13:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,囉嗦！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.50,0:13:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.47,0:13:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信可以的！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.14,0:13:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳是為了什麼而戰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.91,0:13:24.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.45,0:13:26.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要創造一個\N大家都能笑口常開的國家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.05,0:13:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種作夢般的事！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.15,0:13:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是夢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.75,0:13:34.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過就因為是夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.49,0:13:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我第一次來到這座城市
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.23,0:13:38.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇見妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.79,0:13:40.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到靜留姊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.30,0:13:42.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才真正想當一個乙HiME
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.73,0:13:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後我現在成為乙HiME了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.60,0:13:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那時我沒有夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.27,0:13:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定不會成為乙HiME
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.14,0:13:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼亂來的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.47,0:13:54.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要相信它，就會實現
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.34,0:13:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.61,0:13:57.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得相信它會實現而前進
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.38,0:13:59.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然什麼都不會發生的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.31,0:14:02.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為妳沒有真正受挫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.15,0:14:03.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有真正犯錯過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.36,0:14:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.06,0:14:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錯了的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.13,0:14:13.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要再努力思考\N重新來過就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.90,0:14:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣又可以再向前進了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.60,0:14:17.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.73,0:14:19.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經太遲了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.17,0:14:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都太遲了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.72,0:14:40.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.36,0:14:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼妳總是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.56,0:14:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不死心呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.16,0:14:46.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.59,0:14:48.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也喜歡大家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.56,0:14:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我無法放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.30,0:14:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很笨，什麼都不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.14,0:14:57.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，我想更加瞭解妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.37,0:14:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.41,0:15:00.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們再一起重新開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.44,0:15:01.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不好，妮娜？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.55,0:15:06.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能多聊聊就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.51,0:15:08.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟埃爾斯…還有愛莉卡…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.05,0:15:11.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟妳也…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.62,0:15:12.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還來得及啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.62,0:15:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以，妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.39,0:15:17.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞里…香…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.88,0:15:35.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.54,0:15:38.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕，那傢伙失控了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.85,0:15:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去又會跟之前一樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.95,0:15:43.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經太遲了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.38,0:15:46.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了維持謝爾蓋的命\N而不斷運轉的古風琴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.39,0:15:47.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經超過界限了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.89,0:15:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.32,0:15:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在，那古風琴的力量與記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.13,0:15:55.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正流向妮娜的體內
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.80,0:16:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類製作那個所犯下的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.20,0:16:02.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怖與憎根
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.94,0:16:04.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕望
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.44,0:16:07.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就有如過去被稱為\N“純白無暇金剛石”
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.94,0:16:10.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因絕望而徹底染黑一般
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.25,0:16:12.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.91,0:16:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本來以為\N在變成這樣之前可以結束的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.22,0:16:18.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我賭輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.12,0:16:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.62,0:16:21.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.82,0:16:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.46,0:16:29.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.86,0:16:31.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打倒我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.20,0:16:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是現在不打倒我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.14,0:16:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界會完蛋的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.54,0:16:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.91,0:16:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.41,0:16:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果妳…當我是朋友的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.32,0:17:21.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凪，快叫它停下來！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.79,0:17:25.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別過度掙扎了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.62,0:17:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,囉嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.26,0:17:31.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就說沒用了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.06,0:17:34.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴，哪能放棄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.93,0:17:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們絕不放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.00,0:17:43.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳說是不是，愛莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.71,0:17:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，真白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.00,0:18:42.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.20,0:18:47.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳…愛莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.77,0:18:49.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.14,0:18:55.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.19,0:19:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.29,0:19:11.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.20,0:19:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凪·戴·阿爾泰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.86,0:19:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我奉審議會臨時法庭之命
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.00,0:19:20.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將你逮捕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.14,0:19:28.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，快送去加爾德羅貝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.48,0:19:29.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.72,0:19:36.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因為有這種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.97,0:19:55.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然不該存在於這個世界的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.55,0:20:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於抓到妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.05,0:20:11.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞里…香
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.79,0:21:28.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在此對人民宣誓以上事項
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.50,0:21:34.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，最後收尾了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.65,0:21:50.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK，看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.50,0:22:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳還是老樣子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.73,0:22:06.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失敗…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.33,0:22:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次真的要去了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.09,0:22:31.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城堡完工了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.46,0:22:37.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然目前還是座小城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.17,0:22:42.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，要從這裡開始
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.57,0:22:48.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還早呢，以後的路還很長呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.21,0:22:51.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯吧，咪咪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.68,0:22:55.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，愛莉卡，開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.66,0:23:04.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的夢想在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.59,0:23:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以請看著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.47,0:23:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃爾斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.50,0:23:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.09,0:23:35.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳…是？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.13,0:23:47.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.90,0:23:49.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就只是妮娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.60,0:23:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.34,0:23:54.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好，謝爾蓋
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.34,0:23:58.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我的名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.28,0:23:59.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用急
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.88,0:24:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.08,0:24:04.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.15,0:24:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來一次
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.80,0:00:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,

